anted me these two times’ (Genesis 27:36). <i>Jacob</i> is especially common as a Jewish given name, although it also became very popular among the Puritans from the 16th century onwards, and has again been widely used since the 1990s.  Compare  James ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Jaakko was born in 1263, in Finland. He had at least 1 daughter."},"et":{"1263–":"1263–Surnud","1300–Female":"1300–Surnud","1263–Male":"1263–Surnud","1300":"1300","1263":"1263","Suomi":"Soome"},"fi":{"1263–":"1263–Kuollut","1300–Female":"1300–Kuollut","1263–Male":"1263–Kuollut","1300":"1300","1263":"1263","Suomi":"Suomi"},"fr":{"1263–":"1263–Décédé","1300–Female":"1300–Décédée","1263–Male":"1263–Décédé","1300":"1300","1263":"1263","Suomi":"Finlande","lifeSummary":"Jaakko est né en 1263, à Finlande. Il a eu au moins 1 fille."},"de":{"1263–":"1263–Verstorben","1300–Female":"1300–Verstorben","1263–Male":"1263–Verstorben","1300":"1300","1263":"1263","Suomi":"Finnland","lifeSummary":"Jaakko wurde 1263 in Finnland geboren. Er hatte mindestens 1 Tochter."},"ht":{"1263–":"1263–Desede","1300–Female":"1300–Desede","1263–Male":"1263–Desede","1300":"1300","1263":"1263","Suomi":"Finlande"},"hu":{"1263–":"1263–elhunyt","1300–Female":"1300–elhunyt","1263–Male":"1263–elhunyt","1300":"1300","1263":"1263","Suomi":"Finnország"},"id":{"1263–":"1263–Telah Meninggal","1300–Female":"1300–Telah Meninggal","1263–Male":"1263–Telah Meninggal","1300":"1300","1263":"1263","Suomi":"Finlandia"},"it":{"1263–":"1263–Deceduto","1300–Female":"1300–Deceduta","1263–Male":"1263–Deceduto","1300":"1300","1263":"1263","Suomi":"Finlandia","lifeSummary":"Jaakko è nato il nel 1263 nel Finlandia. Lui avuto almeno 1 figlia."},"ja":{"1263–":"1263年–死亡","1300–Female":"1300年–死亡","1263–Male":"1263年–死亡","1300":"1300年","1263":"1263年","Suomi":"フィンランド","lifeSummary":"Jaakkoは1263年にフィンランドで生まれた。彼は少なくとも1人の娘をもうけた。"},"ko":{"1263–":"1263년–사망","1300–Female":"1300년–사망","1263–Male":"1263년–사망","1300":"1300년","1263":"1263년","Suomi":"핀란드","lifeSummary